entry.def: Virgo is one of the twelve signs of the zodiac. Its symbol is a young woman. People who are born approximately between the 23rd of August and the 22nd of September come under this sign.

entry.tran: 出生于室女宫时段的人
entry.def: A Virgo is a person whose sign of the zodiac is Virgo.

means.word_mean: 1. (astrology) a person who is born while the sun is in Virgo
2. a large zodiacal constellation on the equator; between Leo and Libra
3. the sixth sign of the zodiac; the sun is in this sign from about August 23 to September 22
